title: Clutch "Earth Rocker": Rubber Tracks Live
description:
Lead singer Neil Fallon, of the legendary metal group Clutch, ignited the crowd with their track "Earth Rocker" as they headlined the final night of Converse Rubber Tracks Live Brasil.

Venue: Cine Joia
